lender.occupational_info:
The Lithonia Lighting Company was founded in Lithonia, Georgia in 1946 as a manufacturer of household fixtures. Today, Lithonia Lighting has become one of the forefront companies in designing and manufacturing lighting products to suit commercial, industrial, institutional and residential lighting needs.
In putting efficiency to practice, Lithonia Lighting has made a tradition of providing the best value in lighting for over 60 years. It is a subsidiary of Acuity Brands Lighting and has been part of its drive towards excellence in terms of lighting designs and products, and their mission towards green lighting and sustainable building.
Lithonia also maintains a tradition of development and innovation. Part of this tradition is their current development of LED lighting which is proving to be the new frontier for advanced and sustainable lighting solutions. As LED lighting proves to be increasingly viable for a variety of lighting solutions, Lithonia continues its progress for adapting LED technology to make the product more commercially accessible.
Lithonia Lighting’s sustainable lighting solutions take the form of lighting products that meet green standards and codes, conserve energy and will reduce waste. To recognize Lithonia Lighting’s dedication to green lighting, they were named the Energy Star Partner of the Year in 2008. The Energy Star logo on their products indicates that meet stringent energy guidelines that support conservation of energy and help protect the environment.
